    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a pot with 20g <span class=\"text-purple\">[30g] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[40g]</span> <strong>butter</strong> on a low heat</p><p>Once melted, remove the pot from the heat and add the <strong>sriracha</strong> (can’t handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>cider vinegar</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> [2 tsp] <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Stir everything together until it combines and becomes a sauce-like consistency – this is your<strong> buffalo sauce</strong></p>",
